  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"content\"\u003e\n\n\u003carticle\u003e\n\n\t\n \t\n \t\n\n \t\n\n \t\n\t\t\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eThis lemon chive potato salad is a flavorful, simple side dish that can go with just about any weeknight meal. It’s easy and quick to make, packed with chives and parmesan and is great served warm or chilled.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSide dish of the summer!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-4-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"lemon chive potato salad\" width=\"1605\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/06/lemon-chive-potato-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Lemony Chive Potato Salad with Parmesan.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-4-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-4-scaled.jpg 1605w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-4-728x998.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-4-768x1053.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-4-1121x1536.jpg 1121w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-4-1494x2048.jpg 1494w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-4-150x206.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1605px) 100vw, 1605px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIf you love an easy side dish that’s almost potato salad, but not traditional potato salad, I hear you! This lemony, herby potato salad has a delish vinaigrette, tender potatoes, shaved parmesan, fresh chives and garlic. It tastes amazing and is a great weeknight side dish. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"lemon chive potato salad\" width=\"1693\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/06/lemon-chive-potato-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Lemony Chive Potato Salad with Parmesan.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-scaled.jpg 1693w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-728x946.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-768x998.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-1182x1536.jpg 1182w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-1576x2048.jpg 1576w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-150x195.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1693px) 100vw, 1693px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201693%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-scaled.jpg 1693w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-728x946.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-768x998.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-1182x1536.jpg 1182w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-1576x2048.jpg 1576w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-150x195.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-10-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis is an easy recipe today that you can throw together as a side dish for any of your summer meals. It’s simple and looks a little boring but is really packed with flavor. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI’m pretty sure I started this blog based on one belief: I didn’t want mayo in my potato salad. I shared a few different potato salads in those early years that I’m way too horrified to link today, but none of them had a creamy dressing of any sort. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"lemon chive potato salad\" width=\"1740\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/06/lemon-chive-potato-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Lemony Chive Potato Salad with Parmesan.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-scaled.jpg 1740w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-728x920.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-768x971.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-1215x1536.jpg 1215w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-1620x2048.jpg 1620w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-150x190.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1740px) 100vw, 1740px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201740%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-sc