ww.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-2-728x908.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-2-768x958.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-2-1232x1536.jpg 1232w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-2-1642x2048.jpg 1642w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-2-150x187.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1764px) 100vw, 1764px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201764%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-2-scaled.jpg 1764w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-2-728x908.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-2-768x958.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-2-1232x1536.jpg 1232w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-2-1642x2048.jpg 1642w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-2-150x187.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-2-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnyway – this is a little similar to \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2023/06/potato-salad-with-piccata-vinaigrette/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003emy piccata potato salad\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e. Guess what? Back when I shared that recipe, I had finished all the photography for \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/43tfzr9\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEasy Everyday\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e and was dying to share my piccata vinaigrette with you. I tried to be a little unassuming since it has a big recipe in\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/43tfzr9\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e the book\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e – and threw it in with the potato salad! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eP.S. it’s fabulous if you love capers. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"lemon chive potato salad\" width=\"1686\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/06/lemon-chive-potato-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Lemony Chive Potato Salad with Parmesan.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-scaled.jpg 1686w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-728x950.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-768x1002.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-1177x1536.jpg 1177w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-1569x2048.jpg 1569w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-150x196.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1686px) 100vw, 1686px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201686%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-scaled.jpg 1686w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-728x950.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-768x1002.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-1177x1536.jpg 1177w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-1569x2048.jpg 1569w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-150x196.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-6-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSo how do they differ? This potato salad today has a bit of dijon in the dressing. The dressing is more emulsified than the piccata vinaigrette, make it *feel* a little creamier. It’s less briney with no red wine vinegar, onions and capers. It’s also the dressing I use for \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/03/roasted-asparagus/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003emy roasted asparagus\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e, it works double duty! I love sharing a recipe that can be made for two different dishes. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt is a simple lovely potato salad that works when served warm or chilled. It has a ton of flavor, while still being very neutral – you can serve it with almost anything. Lots of lemon, chives and parmesan go with just about anything, right?! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"lemon chive potato salad\" width=\"1701\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/06/lemon-chive-potato-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Lemony Chive Potato Salad with Parmesan.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-scaled.jpg 1701w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-728x942.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-768x994.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-1187x1536.jpg 1187w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-1583x2048.jpg 1583w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-150x194.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1701px) 100vw, 1701px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201701%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-scaled.jpg 1701w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-728x942.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-768x994.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-1187x1536.jpg 1187w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-1583x2048.jpg 1583w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-150x194.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-3-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCan’t you just taste it?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"lemon chive potato salad\" width=\"1686\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/06/lemon-chive-potato-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Lemony Chive Potato Salad with Parmesan.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-scaled.jpg 1686w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-728x950.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-768x1002.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-1177x1536.jpg 1177w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-1569x2048.jpg 1569w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-150x196.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1686px) 100vw, 1686px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201686%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-scaled.jpg 1686w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-728x950.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-768x1002.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-1177x1536.jpg 1177w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-1569x2048.jpg 1569w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-150x196.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/chimichurri-salmon-11-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eLemony Chive Potato Salad with Parmesan\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-99482\" data-recipe-id=\"99482\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-5-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eLemony Chive Potato Salad with Parmesan\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"99482\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e15\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e25\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis lemon chive potato salad is a flavorful, simple side dish that can go with just about any weeknight meal. It\u0026#39;s easy and quick to make, packed with chives and parmesan and is great served warm or chilled.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"recipe-99482-ingredients\" data-recipe=\"99482\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epounds\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epetit yukon gold potatoes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eshaved parmesan cheese,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eplus more if desired\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-chives-0-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-79495118?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003echopped fresh chives\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003elemon chive vinaigrette\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/realemon-100-lemon-juice-15-fl-oz-bottle/-/A-14751839?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003elemon juice\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pompeian-red-wine-vinegar-16-fl-oz/-/A-47846730?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ered wine vinegar\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/dijon-mustard-12oz-market-pantry-8482/-/A-14766261?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003edijon mustard\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-clover-honey-12oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-54436198?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ehoney\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"9\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/spice-world-fresh-whole-garlic-3ct-bag/-/A-14917318?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003egarlic cloves,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efinely minced or pressed\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"10\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-chives-0-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-79495118?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003echopped chives\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"11\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"12\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/extra-virgin-olive-oil-16-9oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77643078?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eextra virgin olive oil\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"recipe-99482-instructions\" data-recipe=\"99482\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99482-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlace the potatoes in a large pot and cover with cold water. Bring to a boil and boil for 10 to 12 minutes, or until the potatoes are fork tender.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99482-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhile the potatoes boil, make the lemon dressing.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99482-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eDrain the potatoes when tender and let cool. Gently slice them in half. Drizzle with some of the lemon vinaigrette.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99482-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdd in the chives, shaved parmesan and a sprinkle of salt and pepper if you wish.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99482-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eToss a few more times to make sure everything is combined. Taste and season one more time if needed. Serve!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003elemon chive vinaigrette\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99482-step-1-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhisk together the lemon juice, vinegar, honey, dijon, garlic, herbs and a big pinch of salt and pepper. Stream in the olive oil while whisking until the dressing is emulsified. This stays great in the fridge for a few days and you can make it ahead of time!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAppetizer\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"lemon chive potato salad\" width=\"1711\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/06/lemon-chive-potato-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Lemony Chive Potato Salad with Parmesan.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-7-scaled.jpg 1711w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-7-728x936.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-7-768x988.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-7-1194x1536.jpg 1194w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-7-1593x2048.jpg 1593w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-salad-7-150x193.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1711px) 100vw, 1711px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201711%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/lemony-potato-